briefdescription.para: The location of the flag on the ground
We need to know the flag persistent id (and keep it in the actual mission) so that other nodes can refer to this particular flag.
The flag asset is offset by about 30 degrees, so we have to reverse that. We're making this a member so that it's easy to spot and change.
